### 1.6 GET Resource Types - Admin (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resource-types
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 1.7 GET Resource Types - Resource Management (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resource-types
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}

###

### 1.8 GET Resource Types - Worker (Expect 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resource-types
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}

###

### 1.9 GET Resource Type By Id - Admin (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resource-types/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 1.10 GET Resource Type By Id - Resource Management (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resource-types/1
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}

###

### 1.11 POST Resource Type - Admin (Expect 403 ForbiddenException System Catalog)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/resource-types
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "string",
  "unitOfMeasure": "kg",
  "category": "FOOD",
  "description": "string"
}

###

### 1.12 PUT Resource Type - Admin (Expect 403 ForbiddenException System Catalog)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/resource-types/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated resource type description"
}

###

### 1.13 DELETE Resource Type - Admin (Expect 403 ForbiddenException System Catalog)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/resource-types/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 1.14 POST Resource Type - Worker (Expect 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/resource-types
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "worker-created-type",
  "unitOfMeasure": "units",
  "category": "OTHER",
  "description": "should be blocked"
}

###

### 1.15 GET Resource Types - Travel Manager (Expect 403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resource-types
Authorization: Bearer {{travelToken}}